title: Wapo: Gay Dating

creator: Wapo y Wapa Ltd - Gay & Lesbian Dating Apps
descriptionHtml:
FREE GAY DATING, CHAT & MEET FOR MEN 18+!

Introducing Wapo, one of the world’s most popular dating apps for you to find, meet and talk to gay, bi and curious men near or far. It’s free and fun to find and meet new men with verified photos - then chat for as long as you like!

VERIFIED PHOTOS! ✅
Finally, a gay dating app that lets you know if the men you chat to are genuine! We verify your pics in minutes without even needing your ID

MEET GUYS YOU’LL LIKE 🔥
Keep the hottest guys close with the favourites section! You can even filter by age, location and more to increase your chances of a good time - who knows where it might lead?

WANT TO KNOW WHO’S INTO YOU? 👀
Who doesn’t?! See exactly who is looking at your profile and find out what they think of you!

UNLIMITED PROFILES & UNLIMITED CHATS 💬
Chat to hot men for as long as you’d like for free and send unlimited voice & video chats - all straight from the app!

WAPO KEEPS YOU SAFE 🔒
Keep your dating life private with an app passcode and verify your photos so everyone knows you’re legit

EXPLORE WITHOUT BORDERS 🌍
Want to broaden your horizons? Explore and chat to men anywhere in the world you choose, meet locals before you go abroad - and translate chats instantly into your language!

VIDEO & AUDIO MESSAGES 📹
Hear what they sound like before you meet, check them out and make chatting even more personal with free unlimited video and audio messages!

MAKING GAY DATING SAFE & FUN 🙌

Meeting new men and chatting should always be a fun and exciting experience. We know how important your safety is - so photos are moderated and verified photos help you be more sure of who you’re talking to. And if you see anything you don’t think should be on the app, you can report it quickly and easily.

At Wapo, we’re working hard to build a genuine and safe network for men everywhere, and we're determined to keep it that way. If you have any questions or concerns - we’re here for you. Just use our in-app live chat for support.

Wapo is the number 1 FREE dating app for meeting and dating queer men near you - or anywhere in the world!

🔑 UNLOCK PREMIUM FEATURES & REMOVE ADS 🔑



Get the ultimate Wapo experience. If you love chatting to men on Wapo, you’ll love this. Get Wapo Premium and we’ll give you total unrestricted access to our app AD FREE and packed with bonus features:

READ RECEIPTS ⏰
Know when they’ve seen your message

UNSEND YOUR MESSAGES 🔏
Sent something you regret? Just delete it - and pretend it never happened ;)

LOAD TOTALLY UNLIMITED MEN NEAR YOU 📍
Free users are limited. You get as many as there are!

COVER YOUR TRACKS 🐾
Remove your track - so that guys don’t know you’ve been checking out their profile

EVEN BETTER FILTERING 💋
Cut through the noise and remove all users who haven’t uploaded any pics

LOCK IT DOWN 🔗
Lock the app with a password and lock your face pics

AND EVEN MORE! 💫
Get live chat support, upload double the amount of pics and activate Do Not Disturb mode!

Terms: http://www.wapoapp.com/terms.htm
